Package jeco.core.operator.evaluator

Class AbstractPopEvaluator

java.lang.Object
jeco.core.operator.evaluator.AbstractPopEvaluator
public abstract class AbstractPopEvaluator extends Object
Abstract class for population evaluators. This class defines the basic structure of a population evaluator. A population evaluator is an object that evaluates a population of solutions. The evaluator is used by the genetic algorithm to evaluate the population of solutions.
